data.description: BRAND NEW INTERIOR PAINT!!! Refreshed interior look for the new year and MOVE IN READY! Nestled amidst a serene backdrop of lush greenery, this charming single-story home is a true sanctuary of comfort and tranquility. Its well-kept yard, adorned with vibrant greenery, provides a picturesque setting. Inside, the heart of the home is a spacious and inviting kitchen, where culinary dreams come to life with ample counter and storage space, alongside a spacious eat-in area that bathes in natural light. The dedicated dining space offers an elegant setting for gatherings, while a separate office space allows you to work or create in peace. The upgraded primary suite is a thoughtful retreat, boasting a soothing ambiance, featuring a spa-like walk-in shower, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Two secondary bedrooms offer versatility and comfort, ensuring plenty of space for family or guests. The living room features a cozy brick fireplace, adding warmth and character to the space. This home offers the perfect blend of serenity and convenience, with each room thoughtfully designed to create a harmonious living experience.
